---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Videos - Quirk Chronicle" description="Explore captivating videos that delve into the quirky facets of human behavior, from subtle social experiments to heartwarming oddities in daily life. Discover the extraordinary through our curated collection.">
  <!-- Hero Section with custom design -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2d3748] to-[#1a202c] opacity-90"></div>
    <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#ff6b6b] bg-[#ff6b6b]/10 rounded-full mb-4 tracking-wider">VIDEO COLLECTION</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">Videos</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 font-light max-w-2xl">Capturing the Quirks in Motion</p>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#ff6b6b] mt-8"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#1a202c] to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#2d3748] mb-6">Welcome to the Gallery of Curiosities</h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-[#ff6b6b] mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-serif italic max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Where the lens of curiosity reveals the hidden rhythms of human eccentricity. Our vintage-inspired collection brings you short films, interviews, and observational pieces that celebrate the peculiar in the everyday.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Immerse yourself in stories that spark wonder and reflection. Each video is a window into the extraordinary moments hidden within ordinary life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Featured Videos Section -->
  <section class="bg-[#f8f9fa] py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#2d3748] mb-4">Featured Videos</h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-[#ff6b6b] mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Video Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] bg-[#2d3748]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#ff6b6b] flex items-center justify-center opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                <i class="fas fa-play text-white text-xl ml-1"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
              <span class="text-white font-serif font-bold text-lg">The Art of Awkward Pauses</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">A silent exploration of those uncomfortable silences in conversations.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Watch as ordinary encounters turn into unexpected theater.</p>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full py-3 bg-[#2d3748] text-white font-medium hover:bg-[#ff6b6b] transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="fas fa-play-circle mr-2"></i> Play Video
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Video Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] bg-[#2d3748]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#ff6b6b] flex items-center justify-center opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                <i class="fas fa-play text-white text-xl ml-1"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
              <span class="text-white font-serif font-bold text-lg">Fidgeting Through History</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">Vintage footage reimagined, showing how small habits have evolved.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">A nostalgic nod to our unchanging quirks.</p>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full py-3 bg-[#2d3748] text-white font-medium hover:bg-[#ff6b6b] transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="fas fa-play-circle mr-2"></i> Play Video
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Video Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] bg-[#2d3748]">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#ff6b6b] flex items-center justify-center opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                <i class="fas fa-play text-white text-xl ml-1"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
              <span class="text-white font-serif font-bold text-lg">Crowd Whispers</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">Audio-visual study of collective human murmurs in public spaces.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Discover the symphony in shared silence.</p>
            <button class="mt-6 w-full py-3 bg-[#2d3748] text-white font-medium hover:bg-[#ff6b6b] transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="fas fa-play-circle mr-2"></i> Play Video
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Vintage Archive Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#2d3748] mb-4">Vintage Archive</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-0.5 bg-[#ff6b6b] mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Explore our collection of restored historical footage capturing human behavior through the decades.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-4 border-white shadow-2xl">
              <div class="bg-gray-200 border-2 border-dashed rounded-xl w-full h-64 md:h-80" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6">
                <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-2">1960s Social Experiments</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm">Rare footage of behavioral studies from the golden age of psychology</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-[#2d3748] mb-4">A Window to the Past</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Our curated archive features restored films from the 1920s through the 1970s, capturing authentic moments of human behavior before the digital age.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              These historical treasures offer unique insights into how social norms and quirks have evolved over time, or remained remarkably consistent.
            </p>
            <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-[#ff6b6b] text-white font-medium hover:bg-[#2d3748] transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center">
              <i class="fas fa-archive mr-2"></i> Explore Archive
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Newsletter CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2d3748] to-[#1a202c] py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-film text-4xl text-[#ff6b6b] mb-6"></i>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4">Stay Updated</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Subscribe to receive notifications about new video releases and exclusive behind-the-scenes content from our filmmakers.
        </p>
        
        <form class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <input 
              type="email" 
              placeholder="Your email address" 
              class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#ff6b6b]"
            />
            <button 
              type="submit" 
              class="px-6 py-3 bg-[#ff6b6b] text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-[#2d3748] transition-colors duration-300 whitespace-nowrap"
            >
              Subscribe
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-4">
          <i class="fas fa-lock mr-1"></i> We respect your privacy. Unsubscribe at any time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>